00:28.820 --> 00:30.155
<i>Population:</i>

00:30.196 --> 00:33.658
<i>2,760.</i>

00:33.700 --> 00:36.411
<i>On the surface,</i>
<i>Iron Lake may seem</i>

00:36.453 --> 00:38.038
<i>like the idyllic snow globe town</i>

00:38.079 --> 00:41.041
