<i>Jim Lindsay.</i>

12:38.466 --> 12:41.093
<i>State your goddamn name.</i>

12:45.306 --> 12:47.600
<i>Dexter. Dexter Morgan.</i>

12:48.934 --> 12:50.269
<i>Hello, Dexter Morgan.</i>

12:50.311 --> 12:51.937
<i>Hello, Chief Bishop.</i>

12:51.979 --> 12:54.607
<i>Where were you the day</i>
<i>Matt Caldwell went missing?</i>

12:54.648 --> 12:57.610
<i>I was... [sighs]</i>
<i>at my cabin, alone.</i>

12:57.651 --> 12:59.820
<i>Okay.</i>

12:59.862 --> 13:02.948
<i>We've determined</i>
<i>that this person</i>

13:02.990 --> 13:05.576
<i>-is Matt Caldwell.</i>
<i>-Yeah.</i>

13:05.618 --> 13:07.161
<i>You remember when I came in</i>

13:07.203 --> 13:08.913
<i>and identified that</i>
<i>distinctive rifle for you?</i>

13:08.954 --> 13:10.164
<i>Yes. You're a good citizen.</i>

13:10.206 --> 13:11.791
<i>I try to be.</i>

13:11.832 --> 13:13.709
<i>Do you really have</i>
<i>no sense of sarcasm?</i>

13:13.751 --> 13:15.628
<i>-No.</i>
<i>- Yes.</i>

13:18.088 --> 13:21.383
<i>I-- We never identified</i>

13:21.425 --> 13:23.803
<i>the second person</i>
<i>out in the woods that morning.</i>

13:25.679 --> 13:27.306
<i>What's interesting is</i>

13:27.348 --> 13:29.642
<i>he has the same build as you,</i>

13:29.683 --> 13:31.393
<i>the same rifle you own.</i>

13:31.435 --> 13:34.814
<i>He even does that same</i>
<i>chin scratch thing you do.</i>

13:34.855 --> 13:36.440
<i>[sighs]</i>

13:36.482 --> 13:38.484
<i>Well, my body size is average,</i>

13:38.526 --> 13:40.319
<i>-which means--</i>
<i>-I know what that means.</i>

13:40.361 --> 13:43.447
<i>And dozens of people in</i>
<i>Iron Lake have that same rifle.</i>

13:43.489 --> 13:45.950
<i>Hell, I personally sold</i>
<i>most of them.</i>

13:45.991 --> 13:48.744
<i>And I don't really know</i>
<i>what you mean about...</i>

13:50.704 --> 13:52.748
<i>...the chin scratch thing.</i>

13:54.542 --> 13:56.335
<i>[Dexter sighs]</i>

13:58.420 --> 14:00.714
<i>You know that Matt Caldwell</i>
<i>shattered his femur</i>

14:00.756 --> 14:02.466
<i>in that boating accident</i>
<i>in Ohio?</i>

14:02.508 --> 14:05.052
<i>I'd heard that. What about it?</i>

14:05.094 --> 14:07.388
<i>[clears throat] These are</i>

14:07.429 --> 14:10.266
<i>the type of screws and plate</i>

14:10.307 --> 14:12.560
<i>used to repair</i>
<i>that sort of fracture.</i>

14:15.646 --> 14:17.314
<i>Okay, and?</i>

14:17.356 --> 14:20.568
<i>And I found them in my mailbox,</i>

14:20.609 --> 14:23.696
<i>along with...</i>

14:23.737 --> 14:25.698
<i>this note.</i>

14:29.743 --> 14:31.036
<i>[scoffs]</i>

14:31.078 --> 14:33.455
<i>Come on, Ange,</i>
<i>you're better than this.</i>

14:35.541 --> 14:38.168
<i>I found this...</i>

14:38.210 --> 14:41.005
<i>in the ashes of your cabin.</i>

14:41.046 --> 14:42.715
<i>ominous music </i>

14:42.756 --> 14:45.885
<i>Remember when I said these</i>
<i>are the type of screws and plate</i>

14:45.926 --> 14:47.845
<i>used on surgeries like Matt?</i>

14:47.887 --> 14:50.306
<i>I was being oblique.</i>

14:50.347 --> 14:52.474
<i>They're not just the type.</i>

14:52.516 --> 14:54.894
<i>These are the actual screws</i>

14:54.935 --> 14:58.188
<i>and plate used on Matt.</i>

14:58.230 --> 15:00.566
<i>They've got serial numbers, so</i>

15:00.608 --> 15:02.610
<i>I called</i>
<i>the Cleveland Clinic and--</i>

15:02.651 --> 15:06.071
<i>And that's why we're here.</i>

15:08.782 --> 15:11.327
<i>And your working theory is...</i>

15:11.368 --> 15:13.704
<i>You went for</i>
<i>your morning walk...</i>

15:13.746 --> 15:16.165
<i>No, I was home all day,</i>
<i>except for work and--</i>

15:16.206 --> 15:18.709
<i>...where you saw Matt</i>
<i>kill the white deer.</i>

15:18.751 --> 15:20.502
<i>You two argued.</i>

15:20.544 --> 15:22.504
<i>Not hard to do, considering</i>
<i>Matt was always an asshole.</i>

15:22.546 --> 15:25.841
<i>Maybe he attacked you.</i>
<i>Maybe it was self-defense.</i>

15:25.883 --> 15:28.344
<i>Or maybe you're jumping to</i>
<i>conclusions that aren't there.</i>

15:28.385 --> 15:30.471
<i>And then Harrison</i>
<i>shows up out of nowhere...</i>

15:31.889 --> 15:33.974
<i>...and you had to get rid</i>
<i>of Matt's body.</i>

15:34.975 --> 15:36.936
<i>And what's your theory</i>
<i>on that one?</i>

15:36.977 --> 15:40.189
<i>You burned it.</i>

15:40.230 --> 15:41.732
<i>Smart.</i>

15:41.774 --> 15:45.069
<i>Until it isn't.</i>

15:45.110 --> 15:47.112
<i>'Cause here's the hitch.</i>

15:47.154 --> 15:49.281
<i>Titanium...</i>

15:52.952 --> 15:54.620
<i>...doesn't melt.</i>

15:54.662 --> 15:57.414
<i>[Dexter]</i> <i>A fact I've become</i>
<i>painfully aware of.</i>

15:57.456 --> 15:59.208
<i>I also have a theory.</i>
<i>You want to hear it,</i>

15:59.249 --> 16:02.962
<i>or are you just gonna tell me</i>
<i>to shut the fuck up?</i>

16:05.297 --> 16:08.384
<i>Kurt lied</i>

16:08.425 --> 16:10.928
<i>about Matt being in New York.</i>

16:10.970 --> 16:14.473
<i>And then he lied about Matt</i>
<i>being at that cabin of his.</i>

16:14.515 --> 16:18.769
<i>And then Kurt stripped that</i>
<i>same cabin down to the studs</i>

16:18.811 --> 16:21.188
<i>a day after your friend,</i>
<i>Molly and I were there.</i>

16:21.230 --> 16:24.650
<i>So, it's not outside the realm</i>
<i>of good, logical theory</i>

16:24.692 --> 16:27.444
<i>that Kurt killed Matt</i>
<i>for any number of</i>

16:27.486 --> 16:29.697
<i>accidental</i>
<i>or intentional reasons.</i>

16:29.738 --> 16:33.367
<i>You yourself said,</i>
<i>"Matt was always an asshole."</i>

16:33.409 --> 16:36.620
<i>Then he needed someone to frame.</i>

16:36.662 --> 16:38.580
<i>Why not the boyfriend</i>
<i>of the chief of police</i>

16:38.622 --> 16:40.791
<i>who just arrested</i>
<i>and humiliated him?</i>

16:40.833 --> 16:41.875
<i>tense music </i>

16:43.002 --> 16:44.753
<i>[sighs]</i>

16:44.795 --> 16:47.006
<i>Hell, Kurt probably</i>
<i>burned down my cabin</i>

16:47.047 --> 16:48.841
<i>just so you'd find</i>
<i>that damn screw.</i>

16:48.882 --> 16:50.968
<i>Don't you see? He set me up.</i>

16:51.010 --> 16:54.680
<i>Ange...</i>

16:54.722 --> 16:57.182
<i>he's trying to get back at you.</i>

16:59.977 --> 17:02.312
<i>Look, you've been under</i>
<i>a ton of pressure lately.</i>

17:02.354 --> 17:04.940
<i>And...</i>

17:04.982 --> 17:08.027
<i>you just found your best</i>
<i>friend's body after so long.</i>

17:08.068 --> 17:10.195
<i>You haven't even had a chance</i>
<i>to grieve for--</i>

17:10.237 --> 17:11.697
<i>Don't you say her name!</i>

17:13.407 --> 17:15.034
<i>Hey, hey.</i>

17:17.327 --> 17:20.247
<i>Why don't we just give Jim--</i>

17:20.289 --> 17:22.875
<i>Dexter-- some time</i>
<i>to gather his thoughts?</i>

17:25.419 --> 17:27.296
<i>We want to keep</i>
<i>this interview clean,</i>

17:27.337 --> 17:29.381
<i>so it stands up in court.</i>

17:43.687 --> 17:45.898
<i>-He's fucking with us.</i>
<i>-Maybe.</i>

17:45.939 --> 17:49.902
<i>But his story seems to be just</i>
<i>on this side of plausible to me,</i>

17:49.943 --> 17:53.238
<i>which means it'll seem plausible</i>
<i>to a jury and the D.A.</i>

17:53.280 --> 17:55.199
<i>You don't know</i>
<i>the full fucking context.</i>

17:55.240 --> 17:57.367
<i>And if there is</i>
<i>a full fucking context,</i>

17:57.409 --> 17:59.078
<i>you might want to fill me in.</i>

18:00.996 --> 18:02.998
<i>I can't.</i>

18:03.040 --> 18:04.750
<i>I got to be sure this time.</i>

18:07.586 --> 18:08.962
<i>-Teddy.</i>
<i>-[Teddy] Chief?</i>

18:09.004 --> 18:10.714
<i>Bring Kurt Caldwell in.</i>

18:10.756 --> 18:12.591
<i>-[Teddy] You got it, boss.</i>
<i>-Anything on the Molly Park APB?</i>

18:12.633 --> 18:15.135
<i>Nothing yet, but I forwarded</i>
<i>the line to my cell.</i>

18:15.177 --> 18:17.554
<i>Okay. Harrison.</i>

18:18.889 --> 18:22.017
<i>Logan will bring you in</i>
<i>to see your father.</i>

18:22.059 --> 18:25.729
<i>Just... five minutes, okay?</i>

18:25.771 --> 18:28.732
<i>Thanks, Ange-- Chief Bishop.</i>

18:30.567 --> 18:32.611
<i>Audrey, you come with me.</i>

18:36.073 --> 18:38.242
<i>Harrison.</i>

18:44.748 --> 18:46.333
<i>Oh.</i>

18:46.375 --> 18:47.960
<i>Sorry. Protocol.</i>

18:57.678 --> 18:59.471
<i>Just hang tight.</i>

19:09.398 --> 19:11.483
<i>[handcuffs clattering]</i>

19:15.487 --> 19:18.323
<i>-I'll give you some privacy.</i>
<i>-Thank you.</i>

19:18.365 --> 19:20.826
<i>What the hell?</i>

19:22.452 --> 19:24.746
<i>Angela thinks</i>
<i>I killed Matt Caldwell.</i>

19:24.788 --> 19:28.083
<i>This has nothing</i>
<i>to do with Kurt. You're safe.</i>

19:28.125 --> 19:30.085
<i>[shaky breathing]</i>

19:30.127 --> 19:32.588
<i>Hey, I've been in tougher spots.</i>

19:32.629 --> 19:34.673
<i>I'll get out of this.</i>

19:34.715 --> 19:36.884
<i>There's no way I'm leaving you.</i>

19:36.925 --> 19:38.594
<i>I promise.</i>

19:38.635 --> 19:40.762
<i>-[Esther] Night, Logan.</i>
<i>-[Logan] Good night, Esther.</i>

19:40.804 --> 19:44.474
<i>Angela's got this... theory,</i>
<i>but it'll never hold up.</i>

19:44.516 --> 19:46.977
<i>We'll be on the road</i>
<i>in a day or two.</i>

19:47.019 --> 19:49.271
<i>Well, what am I supposed</i>
<i>to do till then?</i>

19:49.313 --> 19:50.647
<i>Go find Tess at The Tavern.</i>

19:50.689 --> 19:52.941
<i>She'll feed you</i>
<i>and give you a room.</i>

19:52.983 --> 19:56.028
<i>-Okay.</i>
<i>-Come on, guys.</i>

19:59.114 --> 20:00.866
<i>We'll get through this.</i>

20:02.826 --> 20:04.536
<i>The world needs us.</i>

20:07.831 --> 20:10.209
<i>[sighs] I'll be waiting for you.</i>

20:10.250 --> 20:11.877
<i>And I'll find you.</i>

20:14.213 --> 20:15.797
<i>Hey.</i>

20:15.839 --> 20:18.133
<i>Stay tough.</i>

20:22.221 --> 20:24.890
<i>Turn around.</i>
<i>Hands behind your back.</i>

20:24.932 --> 20:27.059
<i>[handcuffs clicking]</i>

20:30.771 --> 20:32.981
<i>You're a good man, Logan.</i>

20:33.023 --> 20:36.235
<i>I hope you are, too,</i>
<i>for Harrison's sake.</i>

20:37.569 --> 20:40.739
<i>I can't give you</i>
<i>all the details yet, but...</i>

20:42.574 --> 20:46.078
<i>You know how Harrison told you</i>
<i>Jim wasn't his real name?</i>

20:46.119 --> 20:48.372
<i>You said Harrison was high</i>
<i>and didn't mean it.</i>

20:48.413 --> 20:51.458
<i>I didn't know it at the time,</i>

20:51.500 --> 20:54.419
<i>but there's more to that story.</i>

20:54.461 --> 20:57.047
<i>Like what?</i>
<i>What the hell is going on?</i>

20:57.089 --> 20:58.131
<i>[sighs]</i>

20:58.173 --> 20:59.591
<i>Honey,</i>

20:59.633 --> 21:02.469
<i>I know this might be</i>
<i>hard to believe...</i>

21:04.680 --> 21:06.265
<i>...but Jim is dangerous.</i>

21:06.306 --> 21:07.891
<i>Dangerous?</i>

21:07.933 --> 21:09.601
<i>Then why were you dating him?</i>

21:09.643 --> 21:11.311
<i>Why'd you let him</i>
<i>into our house?</i>

21:13.814 --> 21:16.108
<i>Sometimes people</i>
<i>aren't who you think they are.</i>

21:17.067 --> 21:18.694
<i>[door opens]</i>

21:24.825 --> 21:26.618
<i>Wait, Audz.</i>

21:26.660 --> 21:27.911
<i>Go home.</i>

21:27.953 --> 21:30.622
<i>Give Harrison some space.</i>

21:30.664 --> 21:33.041
<i>Why? Is he dangerous too?</i>

21:34.251 --> 21:36.044
<i>No.</i>

21:36.086 --> 21:37.963
<i>Look...</i>

21:38.005 --> 21:40.340
<i>I promise I will tell you</i>
<i>everything tomorrow.</i>

21:53.687 --> 21:55.647
<i>[sighs]</i>

21:55.689 --> 21:58.191
<i>[door opens]</i>

22:00.193 --> 22:02.654
<i>Turn around.</i>
<i>Hands through the slot.</i>

22:04.239 --> 22:06.158
<i>All right.</i>

22:08.994 --> 22:10.871
<i>-[handcuffs clicking]</i>
<i>-[sighs]</i>

22:10.912 --> 22:13.206
<i>This is nuts.</i>

22:13.248 --> 22:15.000
<i>It's really putting me</i>
<i>in touch with my fear</i>

22:15.042 --> 22:17.586
<i>of Harrison growing up</i>
<i>without a father.</i>

22:17.627 --> 22:19.671
<i>I know you've been there.</i>

22:19.713 --> 22:21.757
<i>Go to the far side of the cell.</i>

22:28.013 --> 22:29.765
<i>Tuna.</i>

22:29.806 --> 22:32.392
<i>Huh. Some things never change.</i>

22:34.353 --> 22:36.938
<i>I'm gonna go make sure</i>
<i>that Harrison is set up okay.</i>

22:36.980 --> 22:38.482
<i>I'm not going anywhere.</i>

22:38.523 --> 22:41.860
<i>-[scoffs]</i>
<i>-And thank you.</i>

22:45.864 --> 22:48.033
<i>Sons need their fathers.</i>

22:52.412 --> 22:54.915
<i>[door opens]</i>

23:07.677 --> 23:09.346
<i>Thanks for this.</i>

23:09.388 --> 23:12.391
<i>Oh, you're doing me a favor.</i>
<i>Never fun eating alone.</i>

23:15.435 --> 23:18.480
<i>I know this must be</i>
<i>really, really tough for you.</i>

23:18.522 --> 23:19.981
<i>I'm not the one in jail.</i>

23:20.023 --> 23:22.067
<i>I don't want to see Jim</i>
<i>go away, either.</i>

23:22.109 --> 23:25.237
<i>Look, you got here around</i>
<i>the same time Matt disappeared.</i>

23:25.278 --> 23:27.406
<i>Did you hear or-or see anything</i>

23:27.447 --> 23:29.282
<i>that could help</i>
<i>exonerate your dad?</i>

23:34.621 --> 23:37.582
<i>I-I wasn't in town yet, so I...</i>

23:37.624 --> 23:38.834
<i>can't help.</i>

23:38.875 --> 23:40.419
<i>Are you gonna finish your fries?</i>

23:40.460 --> 23:42.295
<i>[chuckles]</i>

23:50.387 --> 23:52.264
<i>I should head back</i>
<i>to the station.</i>

23:52.305 --> 23:54.266
<i>-Later, Coach.</i>
<i>-Yeah.</i>

23:54.307 --> 23:55.392
<i>[snaps fingers]</i>

23:55.434 --> 23:57.436
<i>Thanks for stopping by.</i>

23:57.477 --> 23:58.937
<i>Oh, and, uh,</i>

23:58.979 --> 24:01.314
<i>try not to eat hamburgers</i>
<i>three meals a day.</i>

24:01.356 --> 24:03.942
<i>I don't want you going up</i>
<i>too many weight classes</i>

24:03.984 --> 24:07.195
<i>before wrestling starts</i>
<i>after New Year's.</i>

24:07.237 --> 24:08.947
<i>-[chuckles]</i>
<i>-[door opens]</i>

24:11.867 --> 24:13.618
<i>[door closes]</i>

24:13.660 --> 24:15.620
<i>slow, somber music </i>

24:31.052 --> 24:33.763
<i>Motherfucker.</i>

24:34.764 --> 24:36.141
<i>[door opens]</i>

24:36.183 --> 24:37.559
<i>[door slams shut]</i>

24:37.601 --> 24:39.561
<i>tense music </i>

24:48.945 --> 24:51.323
<i>[phone ringing]</i>

24:51.364 --> 24:53.158
<i>[grunts]</i>

24:55.368 --> 24:57.579
<i>[grunts]</i>

24:57.621 --> 24:58.830
<i>Batista.</i>

24:58.872 --> 25:00.665
<i>This is Chief Angela Bishop.</i>

25:00.707 --> 25:02.459
<i>We met at that conference</i>
<i>in New York.</i>

25:02.501 --> 25:05.170
<i>Chief Bishop.</i>

25:05.212 --> 25:06.963
<i>Uh... [groans]</i>

25:07.005 --> 25:08.590
<i>I hope I didn't give you</i>
<i>the wrong impression.</i>

25:08.632 --> 25:09.799
<i>You know,</i>
<i>I'm a happily married man.</i>

25:09.841 --> 25:11.468
<i>This is a police matter.</i>

25:11.510 --> 25:13.136
<i>How can I help?</i>

25:13.178 --> 25:15.764
<i>We've had some deaths</i>
<i>in Iron Lake</i>

25:15.805 --> 25:18.975
<i>that are very similar</i>
<i>to an old Miami Metro case.</i>

25:19.017 --> 25:21.311
<i>Do you remember</i>
<i>the Bay Harbor Butcher?</i>

25:21.353 --> 25:23.897
<i>Cristo.</i>
<i>That was a gruesome one.</i>

25:23.939 --> 25:27.442
<i>I looked at the autopsy photos</i>
<i>on the police database.</i>

25:27.484 --> 25:29.819
<i>So, you've seen the, uh--</i>
<i>-The dismemberments.</i>

25:29.861 --> 25:31.321
<i>The whole thing.</i>

25:32.781 --> 25:35.700
<i>What can you tell me</i>
<i>about Sergeant Doakes?</i>

25:35.742 --> 25:38.119
<i>I sat next to him</i>
<i>every day for ten years.</i>

25:38.161 --> 25:39.996
<i>Do you believe that he did it?</i>

25:40.038 --> 25:44.042
<i>I did at the time, but there</i>
<i>were a few other theories.</i>

25:44.084 --> 25:47.045
<i>My, uh, my ex-wife...</i>

25:47.087 --> 25:49.381
<i>My old captain actually thought</i>

25:49.422 --> 25:51.341
<i>it was someone else</i>
<i>in the precinct.</i>

25:51.383 --> 25:52.884
<i>Who?</i>

25:52.926 --> 25:56.221
<i>Dexter Morgan,</i>
<i>but he died years ago.</i>

26:00.225 --> 26:01.726
<i>Chief Bishop?</i>

26:03.019 --> 26:05.188
<i>Check your e-mail.</i>

26:05.230 --> 26:06.898
<i>Okay. Hold on.</i>

26:17.993 --> 26:21.121
<i>tense, dramatic music </i>

26:26.084 --> 26:28.003
<i>When was this taken?</i>

26:28.044 --> 26:29.754
<i>Last month.</i>

26:33.466 --> 26:36.469
<i>Madre de Dios.</i>

26:36.511 --> 26:38.388
<i>Dexter Morgan is alive?</i>

26:38.430 --> 26:40.473
<i>And is sitting in my jail cell.</i>

26:42.767 --> 26:44.769
<i>Can I have your</i>
<i>old captain's name?</i>

26:44.811 --> 26:46.229
<i>I'd like to speak with her.</i>

26:46.271 --> 26:49.608
<i>She was...</i>

26:49.649 --> 26:51.610
<i>she was murdered.</i>

26:54.154 --> 26:56.781
<i>Oh, I'm... I'm so sorry.</i>

26:58.450 --> 27:00.827
<i>Did you ever catch the killer?</i>

27:09.377 --> 27:10.962
<i>[clattering]</i>
<i>-Batista?</i>

27:17.302 --> 27:19.054
<i>Where are you?</i>

27:19.095 --> 27:20.847
<i>I'll be there</i>
<i>first thing tomorrow</i>

27:20.889 --> 27:22.807
<i>with everything I've got.</i>

27:22.849 --> 27:24.476
<i>[door opens]</i>

27:24.517 --> 27:26.519
<i>[phone ringing]</i>

27:26.561 --> 27:27.520
<i>[door closes]</i>

27:27.562 --> 27:29.022
<i>What's up, Teddy?</i>

27:29.064 --> 27:30.982
<i>Kurt Caldwell's</i>
<i>beat feet out of here.</i>

27:31.024 --> 27:33.735
<i>Front door unlocked,</i>
<i>safe empty, closets cleaned out.</i>

27:33.777 --> 27:35.987
<i>And guess what?</i>
<i>His gas truck's here.</i>

27:36.029 --> 27:38.782
<i>Emptied out.</i>
<i>Still smells like fresh gas.</i>

27:38.823 --> 27:40.075
<i>[Angela]</i> <i>Can you stay</i>
<i>at Kurt's overnight?</i>

27:40.116 --> 27:41.534
<i>Just in case he shows up.</i>

27:41.576 --> 27:43.495
<i>You got it, Chief.</i>

27:44.454 --> 27:46.414
<i>slow, dramatic music </i>

27:51.419 --> 27:53.213
<i>Oh... geez.</i>

28:05.684 --> 28:08.395
<i>Put that lying son of a bitch</i>
<i>back in my office.</i>

28:08.436 --> 28:09.688
<i>You're not done for the night?</i>

28:11.356 --> 28:13.441
<i>Oh, I'm just getting started.</i>

28:27.330 --> 28:30.250
<i>[sighs]</i>

28:30.291 --> 28:33.086
<i>You might actually get away with</i>
<i>the Matt Caldwell murder charge.</i>

28:33.128 --> 28:35.338
<i>-Because I didn't do it.</i>
<i>-Oh, you did it, all right.</i>

28:35.380 --> 28:38.049
<i>But I'm not entirely sure</i>
<i>my case will hold up enough</i>

28:38.091 --> 28:41.636
<i>to convince the D.A.</i>
<i>and then the jury.</i>

28:41.678 --> 28:43.680
<i>But hear this and know this.</i>

28:43.722 --> 28:47.475
<i>I will stake my career,</i>
<i>my family,</i>

28:47.517 --> 28:50.103
<i>my everything...</i>

28:50.145 --> 28:51.730
<i>that you're a murderer.</i>

28:51.771 --> 28:53.398
<i>I'm worried about you.</i>

28:53.440 --> 28:57.152
<i>I've got one word for you:</i>

28:57.193 --> 28:58.528
<i>ketamine.</i>

28:58.570 --> 29:01.656
<i>You picked up a healthy--</i>
<i>or unhealthy--</i>

29:01.698 --> 29:03.616
<i>amount from Dr. Patel.</i>

29:03.658 --> 29:05.702
<i>Yeah, I needed it</i>
<i>for Vincent van Goat.</i>

29:05.744 --> 29:06.828
<i>You know he was sick.</i>

29:12.167 --> 29:13.752
<i>Do you recognize this man?</i>

29:13.793 --> 29:15.295
<i>Yeah, it's the piece of shit</i>

29:15.336 --> 29:17.464
<i>who sold the drugs</i>
<i>that almost killed my son.</i>

29:17.505 --> 29:19.507
<i>We...</i>

29:19.549 --> 29:22.135
<i>ended up having</i>
<i>an unfortunate encounter.</i>

29:22.177 --> 29:24.095
<i>About that encounter.</i>

29:24.137 --> 29:27.223
<i>Miles O'Flynn</i>
<i>testified to me that,</i>

29:27.265 --> 29:30.560
<i>"Just before he started pounding</i>
<i>on me, he poked me in the neck.</i>

29:30.602 --> 29:33.563
<i>Like, with a needle</i>
<i>or something."</i>

29:33.605 --> 29:35.732
<i>That was the exact same day</i>
<i>you picked up the ketamine</i>

29:35.774 --> 29:37.567
<i>and several syringes</i>
<i>from Dr. Patel.</i>

29:37.609 --> 29:38.943
<i>You think I drugged him?</i>

29:40.236 --> 29:42.697
<i>I saw Logan question him</i>
<i>in this very station.</i>

29:42.739 --> 29:44.073
<i>There's no way he was drugged.</i>

29:44.115 --> 29:45.700
<i>[Angela]</i>
<i>Only because Logan and Teddy</i>

29:45.742 --> 29:47.494
<i>showed up at Crystal Bar</i>
<i>before you could do it.</i>

29:47.535 --> 29:49.788
<i>God, believe what you</i>
<i>want to believe.</i>

29:51.831 --> 29:53.625
<i>You worked forensics in Miami.</i>

29:53.666 --> 29:56.085
<i>You've seen</i>
<i>autopsy photos before.</i>

29:56.127 --> 29:58.129
<i>Yes and yes.</i>

30:02.759 --> 30:05.136
<i>-[Dexter sighs]</i>
<i>-Jasper Hodge.</i>

30:07.514 --> 30:10.517
<i>Okay, I have no idea</i>
<i>where you're going with this.</i>

30:12.602 --> 30:14.145
<i>It's called...</i>

30:14.187 --> 30:16.272
<i>-[Dexter]</i> <i>A weal mark.</i>
<i>-[Angela] ...a weal mark.</i>

30:16.314 --> 30:18.316
<i>I heard he died</i>

30:18.358 --> 30:20.151
<i>of an accidental</i>
<i>fentanyl overdose.</i>

30:20.193 --> 30:21.653
<i>I can't say I'm sorry.</i>

30:21.694 --> 30:25.573
<i>He also had ketamine</i>
<i>in his system.</i>

30:25.615 --> 30:27.116
<i>And only in his system.</i>

30:27.158 --> 30:29.077
<i>None was found anywhere</i>
<i>in his house or his car.</i>

30:29.118 --> 30:31.162
<i>-Well, I can't speak to that.</i>
<i>-Well...</i>

30:32.664 --> 30:33.832
<i>...then speak to this.</i>

30:33.873 --> 30:36.501
<i>dramatic music </i>

30:42.590 --> 30:45.134
<i>Same weal marks.</i>

30:45.176 --> 30:48.304
<i>Same drug showing up</i>
<i>in their tox report.</i>

30:48.346 --> 30:52.225
<i>It's what we call a pattern.</i>

30:52.267 --> 30:54.811
<i>And it's how I know that you,</i>
<i>Dexter Morgan...</i>

30:56.604 --> 30:58.815
<i>...are the Bay Harbor Butcher.</i>

31:02.443 --> 31:04.195
<i>[scoffs]</i>

31:06.948 --> 31:08.992
<i>The Bay Harbor Butcher</i>

31:09.033 --> 31:12.245
<i>was Miami Metro Detective</i>
<i>Sergeant James Doakes.</i>

31:12.287 --> 31:15.164
<i>Not everyone believes that.</i>

31:17.876 --> 31:20.545
<i>Tomorrow you'll be arraigned</i>
<i>for the murder of Matt Caldwell.</i>

31:20.587 --> 31:22.547
<i>I'm gonna do my best</i>
<i>to see that it sticks</i>

31:22.589 --> 31:24.507
<i>and you get life without parole.</i>

31:24.549 --> 31:26.885
<i>And then,</i>

31:26.926 --> 31:28.303
<i>win or lose,</i>

31:28.344 --> 31:29.637
<i>you're gonna have</i>
<i>a little reunion</i>

31:29.679 --> 31:31.598
<i>with your old friend</i>
<i>Angel Batista.</i>

31:33.266 --> 31:34.309
<i>Yeah.</i>

31:36.436 --> 31:39.230
<i>I met him at that Cop-Con thing.</i>

31:39.272 --> 31:41.900
<i>He's on his way up from Miami</i>
<i>as we speak.</i>

31:44.235 --> 31:46.738
<i>We're gonna extradite</i>
<i>your ass to Florida</i>

31:46.779 --> 31:49.490
<i>where you'll stand trial</i>
<i>as the Bay Harbor Butcher.</i>

31:53.661 --> 31:54.746
<i>Florida.</i>

31:56.289 --> 31:58.750
<i>A state with the motherfucking</i>
<i>death penalty.</i>

31:58.791 --> 32:00.418
<i>[scoffs]</i>

32:06.215 --> 32:08.092
<i>Turn off the camera.</i>

32:10.595 --> 32:12.180
<i>Why the hell would I do that?</i>

32:12.221 --> 32:13.932
<i>I'll talk.</i>

32:17.060 --> 32:20.772
<i>If you've got something to say,</i>
<i>just say it to the camera.</i>

32:26.778 --> 32:28.029
<i>[sighs]</i>

32:36.913 --> 32:38.122
<i>Listening.</i>

32:39.123 --> 32:41.209
<i>What if I told you</i>
<i>you were right?</i>

32:41.250 --> 32:42.460
<i>Well, then,</i>
<i>you'd be admitting to--</i>

32:42.502 --> 32:44.128
<i>I'm not admitting anything.</i>

32:44.170 --> 32:46.714
<i>I'm saying you were right</i>

32:46.756 --> 32:48.633
<i>about Kurt Caldwell.</i>

32:48.675 --> 32:50.802
<i>I can prove it.</i>

32:50.843 --> 32:54.013
<i>Ange, you know in your heart</i>

32:54.055 --> 32:56.015
<i>that Kurt killed Iris.</i>

32:56.057 --> 32:59.018
<i>She was just his first.</i>

33:00.520 --> 33:03.481
<i>He's been active for 25 years.</i>

33:04.941 --> 33:06.693
<i>Very active.</i>

33:06.734 --> 33:08.361
<i>What the hell are you</i>
<i>talking about?</i>

33:08.403 --> 33:09.529
<i>Them.</i>

33:12.115 --> 33:14.659
<i>Go to Kurt's cabin.</i>

33:14.701 --> 33:18.329
<i>100 yards north</i>
<i>of the front door,</i>

33:18.371 --> 33:22.000
<i>under a deadwood pile,</i>
<i>there's a hatch.</i>

33:22.041 --> 33:24.877
<i>Open it, and you'll see</i>
<i>what real evil looks like.</i>

33:24.919 --> 33:27.797
<i>I have dedicated</i>
<i>my entire life to this.</i>

33:27.839 --> 33:29.799
<i>Yeah, and you've been met</i>
<i>with scorn and ridicule</i>

33:29.841 --> 33:32.760
<i>at every turn because you've had</i>
<i>a gut feeling but no proof.</i>

33:32.802 --> 33:34.303
<i>You go to that cabin,</i>

33:34.345 --> 33:37.515
<i>and you'll finally have it.</i>

33:37.557 --> 33:38.850
<i>Proof.</i>

33:49.360 --> 33:50.528
<i>Fuck!</i>

33:57.076 --> 33:58.202
<i>[Logan] You turned off</i>
<i>the camera. What happened?</i>

33:58.244 --> 33:59.454
<i>[Angela]</i>
<i>Put him back in his cell.</i>

33:59.495 --> 34:00.913
<i>I've got to check something out.</i>

34:00.955 --> 34:03.207
<i>-And that would be?</i>
<i>-Just fucking do it.</i>

34:09.797 --> 34:10.965
<i>Harrison.</i>

34:11.007 --> 34:13.801
<i>I-I came to get my stuff,</i>

34:13.843 --> 34:17.096
<i>since it doesn't look like</i>
<i>we're gonna move in together.</i>

34:17.138 --> 34:20.266
<i>Come in. Your stuff's upstairs.</i>

34:22.810 --> 34:24.062
<i>I'm sorry.</i>

34:25.646 --> 34:27.899
<i>I think this is all my fault.</i>

34:29.692 --> 34:31.527
<i>How could this possibly</i>
<i>be your fault?</i>

34:35.239 --> 34:37.200
<i>I told my Mom what you said</i>
<i>at the party.</i>

34:37.241 --> 34:39.035
<i>If I had just kept</i>
<i>my mouth shut--</i>

34:39.077 --> 34:41.037
<i>Th-This-this</i>
<i>isn't because of you.</i>

34:41.079 --> 34:43.498
<i>Then what's going on?</i>

34:43.539 --> 34:45.374
<i>No one will tell me</i>
<i>what's happening.</i>

34:45.416 --> 34:47.126
<i>I know.</i>

34:50.755 --> 34:52.256
<i>I just... [sighs]</i>

34:52.298 --> 34:54.509
<i>want this to be over.</i>

34:54.550 --> 34:57.095
<i>For things to go back to normal.</i>

34:58.638 --> 35:00.932
<i>Normal...</i>

35:00.973 --> 35:03.059
<i>What's that?</i>

35:03.101 --> 35:04.936
<i>Things certainly weren't normal</i>

35:04.977 --> 35:06.854
<i>when you and I were on track</i>
<i>to becoming brother and sister.</i>

35:06.896 --> 35:09.774
<i>[both chuckle]</i>

35:09.816 --> 35:12.610
<i>So, you think this arrest means</i>
<i>our parents are breaking up?</i>

35:12.652 --> 35:14.153
<i>[chuckles]</i>

35:16.656 --> 35:20.034
<i>My dad told me</i>
<i>to wait at The Inn.</i>

35:20.076 --> 35:22.120
<i>But it's really nice to see you.</i>

35:23.412 --> 35:25.456
<i>Well, my mom said</i>
<i>to give you space.</i>

35:26.874 --> 35:29.752
<i>But I guess we don't always have</i>
<i>to do what our parents want.</i>

35:40.346 --> 35:44.142
<i>[Deb] Remember when you thought</i>
<i>not killing was the problem?</i>

35:44.183 --> 35:46.144
<i>How's that going for you?</i>

35:48.688 --> 35:50.815
<i>I can figure this out.</i>

35:50.857 --> 35:53.484
<i>Angela's got her teeth in you.</i>

35:53.526 --> 35:55.153
<i>She's never gonna let go.</i>

35:56.863 --> 35:57.989
<i>You did.</i>

35:58.030 --> 35:59.991
<i>I was your sister.</i>

36:01.325 --> 36:03.119
<i>I trusted you.</i>

36:03.161 --> 36:05.538
<i>I loved you.</i>

36:05.580 --> 36:08.291
<i>Angela's pretty fucking far</i>
<i>from that right now.</i>

36:08.332 --> 36:11.085
<i>Enough!</i>

36:13.880 --> 36:15.673
<i>[whispers] Enough.</i>

36:18.134 --> 36:22.096
<i>Hey, Logan,</i>
<i>can I get some water?</i>

36:22.138 --> 36:24.891
<i>Kind of been doing</i>
<i>a lot of talking today.</i>

36:34.442 --> 36:35.818
<i>Yeah.</i>

36:35.860 --> 36:38.863
<i>You talked Angela</i>
<i>right out of the station.</i>

36:38.905 --> 36:40.531
<i>I'd give anything to know</i>
<i>what you said to her</i>

36:40.573 --> 36:41.908
<i>when the camera was off.</i>

36:41.949 --> 36:43.784
<i>[sighs]</i>

36:43.826 --> 36:46.370
<i>[grunting]</i>

36:46.412 --> 36:49.165
<i>[panting]</i>

36:49.207 --> 36:50.374
<i>[grunts]</i>

36:50.416 --> 36:52.126
<i>I don't want to hurt you.</i>

36:52.168 --> 36:55.171
<i>So, Angela was right about you.</i>

36:55.213 --> 36:57.798
<i>She's a good cop</i>
<i>and so are you,</i>

36:57.840 --> 37:00.718
<i>but this is inevitable.</i>

37:00.760 --> 37:03.429
<i>-So, just give me the keys.</i>
<i>-[grunting]</i>

37:03.471 --> 37:05.765
<i>Do it!</i>

37:05.806 --> 37:07.391
<i>Don't be a hero, Logan.</i>

37:07.433 --> 37:09.185
<i>I just need to get out</i>
<i>and see my son.</i>

37:09.227 --> 37:12.313
<i>Good, good.</i>
<i>Good, good, good, good.</i>

37:16.234 --> 37:18.402
<i>-Don't do that.</i>
<i>-Fuck you.</i>

37:18.444 --> 37:19.862
<i>-[gunshot]</i>
<i>-[bones crack]</i>

37:23.574 --> 37:25.576
<i>[panting]</i>

37:26.869 --> 37:30.248
<i>[Dexter]</i> <i>Damn it, Logan,</i>
<i>you should have listened to me.</i>

37:31.207 --> 37:33.167
<i>tense music </i>

37:49.558 --> 37:51.769
<i>[grunting]</i>

37:55.982 --> 37:58.693
<i>[dialing]</i>

37:58.734 --> 37:59.902
<i>[line ringing]</i>

37:59.944 --> 38:01.988
<i>[vibrating]</i>

38:09.537 --> 38:11.539
<i>Yo, Coach. Is my dad okay?</i>

38:11.580 --> 38:12.832
<i>[Dexter]</i>
<i>It's me.</i>

38:12.873 --> 38:15.376
<i>Wh-- Dad?</i>

38:15.418 --> 38:16.836
<i>Where-where are you?</i>

38:16.877 --> 38:18.879
<i>Come downstairs.</i>
<i>Meet me in front of the station.</i>

38:18.921 --> 38:21.924
<i>Um, I'm at-I'm at Audrey's.</i>

38:21.966 --> 38:23.801
<i>Okay, that's actually better.</i>

38:23.843 --> 38:25.219
<i>Grab all your stuff.</i>

38:25.261 --> 38:26.804
<i>My truck is in</i>
<i>Angela's driveway.</i>

38:26.846 --> 38:28.347
<i>The key's in the cupholder.</i>

38:28.389 --> 38:30.599
<i>Meet me where we found</i>
<i>the white deer.</i>

38:30.641 --> 38:32.435
<i>I got it.</i>

38:32.476 --> 38:35.521
<i>Sun's coming up. Go.</i>

38:35.563 --> 38:37.857
<i>Now.</i>

38:45.448 --> 38:46.782
<i>[alarm chirps]</i>

38:52.997 --> 38:55.166
<i>[engine starts]</i>

39:20.024 --> 39:22.318
<i>ominous music </i>

39:32.036 --> 39:34.121
<i>[coughs]</i>

39:36.665 --> 39:38.709
<i>[sniffles]</i>

39:45.341 --> 39:47.385
<i>[panting]</i>

40:18.457 --> 40:21.502
<i>Oh! [gasps]</i>

40:21.544 --> 40:23.087
<i>Annie Kurtz?</i>

40:24.255 --> 40:25.923
<i>Jennifer Nùñez.</i>

40:25.965 --> 40:28.551
<i>Oh, my... oh, my God.</i>

40:28.592 --> 40:30.636
<i>[crying]</i>

40:34.098 --> 40:35.599
<i>Shannon Luu.</i>

40:35.641 --> 40:38.727
<i>[gasping]</i>

40:38.769 --> 40:40.187
<i>Lily Kosnicki.</i>

40:40.229 --> 40:41.272
<i></i>
<i>-[dialogue inaudible]</i>

40:41.313 --> 40:43.274
<i>sinister music </i>

40:48.028 --> 40:48.988
<i>[gasps]</i>

40:49.029 --> 40:50.448
<i>Molly.</i>

40:50.489 --> 40:52.324
<i></i>
<i>-[dialogue inaudible]</i>

40:58.956 --> 41:00.791
<i>intense, dramatic music </i>

41:02.376 --> 41:04.420
<i>[crying]</i>

41:16.682 --> 41:19.101
<i>Logan. Logan, are you there?</i>

41:19.143 --> 41:21.145
<i>Logan, do you copy? Pick up.</i>
<i>-[radio static]</i>

41:21.187 --> 41:23.314
<i>[Dexter]</i>
<i>That was faster than I expected.</i>

41:23.355 --> 41:26.775
<i>[Angela]</i>
<i>Logan. We have multiple bodies.</i>

41:26.817 --> 41:29.820
<i>[engine revs]</i>

41:29.862 --> 41:31.947
<i>Oh, fuck.</i>

41:31.989 --> 41:33.949
<i>tense music </i>

41:36.494 --> 41:38.537
<i>[ringtone playing]</i>

41:46.670 --> 41:47.963
<i>Fuck!</i>

41:48.005 --> 41:50.174
<i>[shaky breathing]</i>

41:50.216 --> 41:52.468
<i>[phone ringing]</i>

41:55.221 --> 41:56.388
<i>'Sup, Chief?</i>

41:56.430 --> 41:58.516
<i>Get me state troopers, CSI,</i>

41:58.557 --> 42:00.351
<i>the coroners,</i>
<i>the motherfucking FBI.</i>

42:00.392 --> 42:02.019
<i>I found something like 30 bodies</i>

42:02.061 --> 42:04.146
<i>at the Caldwell property</i>
<i>on Stearn Road.</i>

42:04.188 --> 42:05.856
<i>I need all the backup I can get</i>

42:05.898 --> 42:07.650
<i>before this place turns into</i>
<i>a fucking media frenzy.</i>

42:07.691 --> 42:10.319
<i>Holy shit. Got it. On it.</i>

42:10.361 --> 42:12.988
<i>Wait, Teddy. [panting]</i>

42:13.030 --> 42:15.699
<i>Have you heard from Logan</i>
<i>in the past hour?</i>

42:15.741 --> 42:18.702
<i>No. I think he's still</i>
<i>at the station with Jim.</i>

42:19.954 --> 42:22.831
<i>Fuck! Fuck!</i>

42:26.710 --> 42:28.754
<i>[crying]</i>

42:49.441 --> 42:51.485
<i>[panting]</i>

42:54.738 --> 42:56.740
<i>dramatic music </i>

43:26.353 --> 43:28.314
<i>slow, somber music </i>

43:36.655 --> 43:38.240
<i>Dad.</i>

43:38.282 --> 43:41.201
<i>Grab your stuff</i>
<i>and leave the truck. Let's go.</i>

43:41.243 --> 43:43.120
<i>Are you hurt?</i>

43:43.162 --> 43:44.997
<i>No. I'm okay. Come on.</i>

43:46.332 --> 43:47.958
<i>Whose blood is that?</i>

43:50.127 --> 43:51.962
<i>I'll explain everything later.</i>
<i>We need to go.</i>

43:52.004 --> 43:53.172
<i>Now.</i>

43:59.011 --> 44:00.638
<i>Wait.</i>

44:00.679 --> 44:03.724
<i>You called me</i>
<i>from Logan's phone.</i>

