44:21.075 --> 44:23.243
<i>Coach Logan's a good person.</i>

44:23.285 --> 44:26.705
<i>He wouldn't cooperate.</i>

44:28.707 --> 44:31.293
<i>It's the only way I could</i>
<i>get back to you. Come on.</i>

44:33.629 --> 44:36.006
<i>Look, we'll talk</i>
<i>about everything,</i>

44:36.048 --> 44:37.508
<i>I promise,</i>

44:37.549 --> 44:40.302
<i>but this is it.</i>
