44:45.641 --> 44:47.309
<i>Shut up.</i>

44:47.351 --> 44:49.186
<i>You don't really care</i>
<i>about saving anybody, do you?</i>

44:49.228 --> 44:52.648
<i>You're just feeding</i>
<i>this-this Dark Passenger.</i>

44:52.690 --> 44:54.858
<i>[scoffs]</i>
<i>I-It's not even a passenger.</i>

44:54.900 --> 44:56.360
<i>It's fucking driving.</i>

44:56.402 --> 44:57.945
<i>And you like it.</i>

44:57.986 --> 45:00.489
<i>You slashing Ethan</i>

45:00.531 --> 45:02.491
<i>and breaking</i>
<i>that wrestler's arm--</i>

45:02.533 --> 45:04.201
<i>that's your own darkness.</i>

45:05.577 --> 45:07.079
<i>You're just like me, buddy.</i>

45:07.121 --> 45:08.747
<i>No.</i>

45:08.789 --> 45:11.083
<i>I wanted to be like you...</i>

45:11.125 --> 45:13.001
<i>so bad.</i>

45:13.043 --> 45:16.672
<i>But m-my anger</i>
<i>isn't because I'm like you.</i>

45:16.714 --> 45:19.383
<i>My-my anger is because of you.</i>

45:19.425 --> 45:21.719
<i>Of-of course I'm angry.</i>

45:21.760 --> 45:25.264
<i>You didn't just make</i>
<i>the decision to abandon me once.</i>

45:25.305 --> 45:27.349
<i>You made that decision</i>
<i>every single day</i>

45:27.391 --> 45:30.060
<i>you stayed away for ten years!</i>

45:37.276 --> 45:40.988
<i>Well, I'm still your dad,</i>
<i>and I'm here now.</i>

45:41.029 --> 45:42.781
<i>I'm right here.</i>

45:45.117 --> 45:47.995
<i>Just come with me, buddy.</i>

45:52.624 --> 45:54.001
<i>I can stop.</i>

45:54.042 --> 45:56.503
<i>I can do it, with your help.</i>

45:56.545 --> 45:58.756
<i>I'm not your fucking caretaker.</i>

45:58.797 --> 46:00.257
<i>I'm your goddamn son.</i>

46:00.299 --> 46:01.759
<i>I want...</i>

46:09.057 --> 46:11.518
<i>I need to be with you.</i>

46:16.690 --> 46:18.901
<i>You have to turn yourself in.</i>

46:20.736 --> 46:22.446
<i>There's no other way.</i>

46:26.617 --> 46:29.161
<i>If I do,</i>
<i>I get the death penalty.</i>

46:31.413 --> 46:33.749
<i>Maybe you deserve it.</i>

46:33.791 --> 46:35.751
<i>somber music </i>

46:37.795 --> 46:39.838
<i>[scoffs softly]</i>

46:45.052 --> 46:46.804
<i>Okay.</i>

46:50.849 --> 46:52.893
<i>You don't have to come with me.</i>

46:56.355 --> 46:58.524
<i>But I can't stay here.</i>

47:05.072 --> 47:07.616
<i>[rifle cocks]</i>

47:10.410 --> 47:12.913
<i>Would my mom still be alive</i>
<i>if it weren't for you?</i>

47:12.955 --> 47:16.458
<i>Would Aunt Deb still be alive?</i>

47:16.500 --> 47:19.878
<i>And me--</i>
<i>would I be so fucked-up?</i>

47:19.920 --> 47:22.840
<i>Open your eyes</i>
<i>and look at what you've done!</i>

47:25.425 --> 47:27.052
<i>dramatic music </i>

47:38.313 --> 47:39.565
<i>You're right.</i>

47:39.606 --> 47:41.608
<i>I don't...</i>

47:41.650 --> 47:44.736
<i>I don't want to be right.</i>

47:44.778 --> 47:46.488
<i>I...</i>

47:46.530 --> 47:49.825
<i>I just-- I want to be normal.</i>

47:49.867 --> 47:51.827
<i>somber music </i>

48:04.548 --> 48:07.885
<i>I'm sorry for everything</i>
<i>I've done to you.</i>

48:12.055 --> 48:14.224
<i>You deserve better.</i>

48:18.270 --> 48:19.897
<i>A better life.</i>

48:23.483 --> 48:24.985
<i>A better father.</i>

48:32.159 --> 48:34.244
<i>[shaky breathing]</i>

48:38.749 --> 48:41.126
<i>You have to take the safety off.</i>

48:45.964 --> 48:47.591
<i>Just like I showed you.</i>

48:47.633 --> 48:49.593
<i>tense music </i>

48:58.143 --> 49:00.979
<i>[sighs]</i>

49:01.021 --> 49:03.231
<i>This is the only way out.</i>

49:09.404 --> 49:10.906
<i>For both of us.</i>

49:17.663 --> 49:20.999
<i>Now...</i>

49:21.041 --> 49:23.418
<i>deep breath.</i>

49:32.386 --> 49:35.138
<i>I've never really felt love.</i>

49:37.849 --> 49:41.436
<i>Real love.</i>

49:41.478 --> 49:43.188
<i>Until now.</i>

49:44.982 --> 49:46.984
<i>[gunshot]</i>

49:48.652 --> 49:50.612
<i>slow, somber music </i>

50:03.625 --> 50:05.544
<i>You did good.</i>

