<i>[footsteps approaching]</i>

50:54.051 --> 50:55.719
<i>Drop the rifle! On your knees!</i>

50:55.761 --> 50:58.388
<i>Hands where I can see them!</i>

50:58.430 --> 51:01.266
<i>I'm-- I stopped--</i>
<i>He-he killed Coach Logan.</i>

51:01.308 --> 51:02.726
<i>I know.</i>

51:02.768 --> 51:05.103
<i>It's okay. You can get up.</i>

51:25.791 --> 51:27.459
<i>Okay.</i>

