<i>Go through town,</i>
<i>just past the Truck Stop</i>

51:34.299 --> 51:36.343
<i>is the entrance to I-86 west.</i>

51:36.384 --> 51:38.804
<i>Go, and never come back here.</i>

51:41.973 --> 51:43.016
<i>Harrison.</i>

51:44.434 --> 51:47.354
<i>You need to do this now.</i>

51:53.777 --> 51:56.905
<i>Uh, tell Audrey I said goodbye.</i>

51:56.947 --> 51:58.115
<i>I can't.</i>

51:58.156 --> 51:59.157
<i>Why?</i>

51:59.199 --> 52:01.785
<i>Because I haven't seen you.</i>

