<i>slow, dramatic music </i>

52:47.664 --> 52:49.916
<i>This is Chief Bishop.</i>

52:49.958 --> 52:53.044
<i>I'm calling to report</i>
<i>an officer-involved shooting.</i>

52:56.298 --> 52:58.008
<i>[Dexter]</i>
<i>My dearest Hannah,</i>

52:58.049 --> 53:01.678
<i>this is the most difficult</i>
<i>letter I'll ever write.</i>

53:04.347 --> 53:06.683
<i>-[engine starts]</i>
