53:09.227 --> 53:13.148
<i>and I believe</i>
<i>that's for the best.</i>

53:13.190 --> 53:16.484
<i>I'd give anything to see</i>
<i>you and Harrison again.</i>

53:16.526 --> 53:19.529
<i>To see him smile.</i>

53:19.571 --> 53:21.573
<i>To hold him.</i>

53:21.615 --> 53:23.783
<i>I celebrate his birthday</i>
<i>in my heart.</i>

53:23.825 --> 53:25.243
<i>"I Should Live in Salt"</i>
<i>by The National </i>

53:25.285 --> 53:28.246
<i>He is and always will be</i>
<i>my phantom limb.</i>

