<i>But you're not right </i>

54:19.714 --> 54:23.009
<i>[Dexter]</i>
<i>I want what every father wants:</i>

54:23.051 --> 54:26.054
<i>for his child to be happy.</i>

54:27.806 --> 54:30.600
<i>To live and love without fear.</i>

54:31.851 --> 54:33.895
<i>To share his gifts</i>
<i>with the world.</i>

54:33.937 --> 54:35.730
<i>I should leave it alone </i>

54:35.772 --> 54:38.316
<i>But you're not right </i>

54:39.567 --> 54:41.236
