<i>[Dexter]</i>
<i>This is not an easy decision.</i>

55:05.427 --> 55:08.596
<i>Sometimes I wish</i>
<i>the hurricane had taken me,</i>

55:08.638 --> 55:12.559
<i>released me from the burden</i>
